{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/nginx/issue/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"升高"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"eef90376-fefc-5ea2-b4d0-80726dc9c6c0","excerpt":"1 服务器重启后，理论上 nginx 处于关闭状态，但是开启 nginx 后报错，现在还未解 执行  提示 80 端口被占用，通过  可找到相应的进程 id，然后 kill 掉。再  ok。","html":"<p>1 服务器重启后，理论上 nginx 处于关闭状态，但是开启 nginx 后报错，现在还未解</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">nginx <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-s</span> reload\nnginx: <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>error<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> invalid PID number <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/run/nginx.pid\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>执行 <code class=\"language-text\">nginx -s reload</code> 提示 80 端口被占用，通过 <code class=\"language-text\">lsonf -i :80</code> 可找到相应的进程 id，然后 kill 掉。再 <code class=\"language-text\">nginx -s relaod</code> ok。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"nginx 问题记录","date":"July 25, 2022","description":"nginx 使用问题记录"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/react/syntheticEvent/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"React 合成事件"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tools/mac/进程/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"mac 常用命令"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"eef90376-fefc-5ea2-b4d0-80726dc9c6c0","previousPostId":"a2023517-329c-5e28-a388-cbae1dcfd53f","nextPostId":"e8c3bb07-f595-54a4-ac08-75f46a2014c3"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383"]}